
mixin card(data)
    div(class='card-body')
        div(class='card__carousel')
            div(class='card__carousel-switcher')
        div(class='card__info')
            div(class='card__info-row')
                div(class='card__number')
                    |№
                    |
                    span(class='card__text_bold-accent') #{data.number}
                    span(class='card__text_accent') люкс 
                div(class='card__cost')
                    span(class='card__text_bold-accent-faded') 9 900р
                    |в сутки
            img(class='card__info-row card__info-separator' src=require("/src/views/components/card/border-line.svg"))
            div(class='card__info-row')
                div(class="card__stars") *****
                div(class="card__reviews")
                    span(class="card__text_bold-accent-faded") 65 
                    |отзывов